name: Christmas Card with sausage dog illustration
description:
My younger sister is obsessed with sausage dogs. When she finally gets one his name will be Cecil. This design is inspired by her, it's an illustration of her perfect Christmas present.

An A6 card (105 x 148mm), packaged with a white envelope in a cello bag.

Digitally printed in the UK on FSC Certified card.

The card is blank inside for your message.

If you'd like to buy 6 or more cards (whether all the same design or a mixture of the designs I stock) message me, let me know which you'd like and how many and I can offer a discount.

I've done my best to photograph the card accurately but the colors that you see on your screen may vary slightly from the actual printed colors (possibly looking a little lighter on screen).

name: Frog limited edition print. Frog illustration.
description:
Aristophanes the little blue frog is the next in my small pets with BIG names series, and possibly the cutest (just don't tell Constantine the Chameleon). He was inspired by a trip to the reptile house at London Zoo. In real life little blue frogs are pretty poisonous so you might not really want one as a pet. Much better to buy this print instead!

This is a high quality giclee print on thick 255gsm stock. Both inks and paper are archival quality and are fade resistant for 70-80 years. The print is signed and is a limited edition of 50.

The print is A5 (210x148 mm) plus a 25mm white border so that it's a nice dinky size and easy to frame. Aristophanes and Constantine would make a lovely set if you are looking for a pair of prints. 

The print is sold unframed to keep p&p prices down and to allow you to frame it as you want.

I've done my best to photograph the print accurately but the colors that you see on your screen may vary slightly from the actual printed colors (possibly looking a little lighter on screen).

Copyright 2011 HelloWilson.

name: A Tangle of Octopuses tote
description:
If only we all had 8 arms. Carrying all those annoying bits and bobs would be so much easier. For those of us stuck with just one pair of hands here's a handy cotton bag. Great for trips to the supermarket or perhaps a day out at the aquarium.

The design is a print of an original hand drawn illustration inspired by the collective noun 'a tangle of octopuses'. The bag is printed on one side only.

The bag measures 38cm(w) x 43cm(h) with 63cm handles. It's 100% cotton, fair trade and made in a carbon neutral factory. Cotton bags make great alternatives to plastic bags!

Copyright 2010 HelloWilson.
